{"tid":1389172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推晒所有圍村巴絲上水舉報村內有爆炸品","createTime":"2019-07-30T23:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T00:48:42.000Z","uid":51105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce5324fa7829ef560a453150b565a27b1692e39","tid":1389172,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:59:35.000Z","msg":"根據香港法律第二百九十五章危險品條例第六條，非法藏有煙花爆竹的最高刑罰為罰款二萬五千元及監禁六個月。<br />\n<br />\n危險品（一般）規例第五十九條亦訂明，未領有許可証燃放或致使他人燃放煙花爆竹屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n任何人觸犯此項規定如循簡易程序定罪，可被罰款二千元。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又說：「根據香港法律第二百二十八章簡易治罪條例第四（十四）條，任何人如肆意或疏忽地發射火器，可被罰款五百元或入獄三個月。」"},{"pid":"e226f6c3e8a5f2c70905c651591086d2a0afadf7","tid":1389172,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454f3e7e94d885512d21fe9b8abad22e62ec8cf8","tid":1389172,"uid":262091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:01:48.000Z","msg":"仲要僭建啊<br />\nhk樓宇安全靠巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bd.gov.hk/doc/tc/resources/pamphlets-and-videos/VHWUBW_b.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bd.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2Ftc%2Fresources%2Fpamphlets-and-videos%2FVHWUBW_b.pdf&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=205480cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bd.gov.hk/doc/tc/resources/pamphlets-and-videos/VHWUBW_b.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入黎幫手一人一信<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對黑警加人工! </span></